The paper deals with graph problems and their analysis in the context of parameterized streaming algorithms. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), followed by cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), cs.CC (Computational Complexity), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), and cs.AL (Computational Geometry).
